    <title>SAP integration CBS handles the sending status change of the payment file</title>
    <updated>2024-08-15T14:13:53.829000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>HS9</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1472768</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;1、不能更该状态&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;处理付款文件APP:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="图片1.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/152454iD9B4D1C7E906BE69/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="图片1.png" alt="图片1.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;发送给第三方支付平台CBS后，文件状态改为“已发送”，&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;CBS回传状态怎样映射到SAP，方便重处理&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;处理发票的付款项目APP&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="图片2.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/152460iBC5F1E9CFB6A191B/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="图片2.png" alt="图片2.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="图片3.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/152462i69D975F397021981/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="图片3.png" alt="图片3.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;2、无法重新发送未付款成功的行项目&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;付款文件状态的API怎么获取，需要让CBS返回付款状态，映射SAP付款状态&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="图片4.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/152463i0720012EBF2B104D/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="图片4.png" alt="图片4.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/financial-management-q-a/sap-integration-cbs-handles-the-sending-status-change-of-the-payment-file/qaq-p/13796088"/>
    <published>2024-08-15T14:13:53.829000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
